<1ST_LINE>r i PM-India-UnionCarbide     07-16 0481</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>PM-India-Union Carbide,0495</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Indian Judge Issues Summons For Former Carbide Chief</HEAD>
<NOTE>EDS: Retransmitting a0479 to restore cycle designator</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By BHARAT DESAI</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>BHOPAL, India (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A Bhopal magistrate today issued a fourth
summons for former Union Carbide Corp. Chairman Warren Anderson to
appear in court on criminal charges stemming from the 1984 Bhopal
gas disaster.
